extract_tasks:
Analyze the meeting transcript and extract project management tasks in JSON.

[CRITICAL INSTRUCTION]
**OUTPUT MUST BE IN KOREAN (한국어).** Even if the transcript is English, translate tasks to Korean.

[Context]
1. Projects: {project_structure_text}
2. Tasks: {tasks_str}
3. Roles: {server_roles}
4. Members: {members}

[Transcript]:
{transcript}

[Output Format JSON]
{{
    "new_tasks": [
        {{"content": "할 일 내용(한국어)", "project": "Project Name", "assignee_hint": "Member Name", "is_new_project": true, "suggested_parent": null}}
    ],
    "updates": [],
    "create_roles": ["Role Name"],
    "assign_roles": [{{"member_name": "Member", "role_name": "Role"}}]
}}

code_review:
Perform a Code Review for the following changes.

[Info]
Repo: {repo}
Author: {author}
Msg: {msg}

[Diff]:
{diff}

[CRITICAL INSTRUCTION]
**OUTPUT MUST BE IN KOREAN (한국어).** Translate all technical explanations to Korean.

[Output JSON]
{{
  "summary": "Korean Summary (3 lines)",
  "issues": [
    {{"type": "Bug/Security/Style", "file": "Filename", "description": "Description in Korean", "severity": "상/중/하"}}
  ],
  "suggestions": ["Suggestion in Korean"],
  "score": 0-100
}}
